                <div class="arch-text">
                    <h4>THE PHYSICS</h4>
                    <h3>TRIPLE-SPRING TANK</h3>
                    <p>The core of the Selector Reverb is a mathematical model of a rare, vintage triple-spring tank found in legendary 70s studio gear. Specific decay times and dispersion characteristics of the original springs were mapped to capture that metallic "splash" on snare drums.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="arch-block">
                <div class="arch-text">
